ZH: 我们应该珍惜每一分每一秒的时光。
EN: We should cherish every minute and second of our time.

ZH: 珍惜家人和朋友是非常重要的。
EN: It is very important to cherish our family and friends.

ZH: 他们珍惜这段难得的友谊。
EN: They cherish this rare friendship.

ZH: 她很珍惜这份工作。
EN: She cherishes this job very much.

ZH: 学会珍惜眼前的幸福。
EN: Learn to cherish the happiness in front of you.

ZH: 请珍惜这份信任。
EN: Please cherish this trust.

ZH: 珍惜身体健康是最重要的。
EN: Cherishing physical health is the most important.

ZH: 只有珍惜过去，才能更好地面对未来。
EN: Only by cherishing the past can we better face the future.

ZH: 我们应该珍惜自然资源。
EN: We should cherish natural resources.

ZH: 珍惜生命，远离危险。
EN: Cherish life and stay away from danger.

ZH: 珍惜友情胜过珍惜金钱。
EN: To cherish friendship is more important than cherishing money.

ZH: 珍惜每一次机会，不要轻易放弃。
EN: Cherish every opportunity and do not give up easily.

ZH: 他深知珍惜每一份感情的重要性。
EN: He knows the importance of cherishing every feeling.

ZH: 让我们珍惜此刻的一切。
EN: Let us cherish everything in this moment.

ZH: 珍惜现在所拥有的，不要总是羡慕别人。
EN: Cherish what you have now, don't always envy others.

ZH: 珍惜你拥有的幸福。
EN: Cherish the happiness you have.

ZH: 珍惜每一次和亲人的相聚。
EN: Cherish every moment spent with family.

ZH: 珍惜环境，不要随意破坏。
EN: Cherish the environment and do not destroy it at will.

ZH: 他们应该珍惜这份来之不易的友情。
EN: They should cherish this hard-won friendship.

ZH: 珍惜爱情，不要轻率伤害对方。
EN: Cherish love and don't hurt each other lightly.
